  "body": "\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: if issues are coming for the active chat when you are browsing profile for example - after switching back to \"Home\" screen messages are not marked as read and you should manually reselect it to mark messages as read.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nMessages are read after switching back to Home\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nCounter shows unread messages\r\n<img width=\"339\" alt=\"unr\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/45546580-6d7d5b00-b826-11e8-9cbf-d7277ece8794.png\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status-desktop\r\n- Log in\r\n- Join to any public chat (i.e. #test)\r\n- Switch to #test\r\n- Switch to Profile\r\n- Send some messages to #test channel from  mobile\r\n- Go back to Home in Desktop to read #test\r\n \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: nightly 14/09/18\r\n* Operating System: Mac OSx\r\n* Video: http://take.ms/2LqmF\r\n\r\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://api.monosnap.com/rpc/file/download?id=Bi15sH5ERQhvEzcqsdEB2x2ou5kX6e&type=preview\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div>Monosnap screenshot tool</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://monosnap.com/file/Bi15sH5ERQhvEzcqsdEB2x2ou5kX6e\">File \"screencast 2018-09-14 13-27-50.mp4\"</a></strong></div><div>Monosnap â€” the best tool to take & share your screenshots.</div></blockquote>",
